---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Healthie.FYI">
	<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-20">
		<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">About Healthie.FYI</h1>

		<div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate prose-headings:font-serif prose-a:text-teal-600">
			<p class="lead text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">
				We are dedicated to bringing you the latest insights at the intersection of health, fitness, and technology.
			</p>

			<p>
				In an era where AI and biotechnology are rapidly transforming how we understand our bodies, keeping up with the latest developments can be overwhelming.
				<strong>Healthie.FYI</strong> cuts through the noise to deliver curated, evidence-based news and analysis.
			</p>

			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				To empower individuals with knowledge about the future of health and fitness. We believe that understanding the tools and science of tomorrow helps us live better today.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
